            "notes": "This deck focuses on utilizing aggressive tactics with Spider-Man 2099 as the commander. It includes a mix of powerful creatures, efficient removal spells, and disruptive counterspells to control the board and apply pressure on the opponent. The deck aims to quickly develop a board presence and maintain tempo advantage by leveraging cards like True-Name Nemesis and Thundering Falls. It also incorporates card advantage engines like Vendilion Clique and Snapcaster Mage to generate value and outmaneuver the opponent. The mana base is optimized for consistency and flexibility, allowing the deck to smoothly curve out and support its varied spell options. Overall, the deck is designed to overwhelm the opponent with swift and decisive plays while maintaining strategic control of the game."
